@startuml Technology Architecture
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

title Node.js Technology Architecture (TOGAF Technology Architecture)

package "Application Technology Layer" {
  [Node.js Core] as NodeCore
  [JavaScript API] as JSAPI
  [Built-in Modules] as BuiltinModules
}

package "Runtime Technology Layer" {
  [V8 JavaScript Engine] as V8Engine
  [JIT Compiler] as JITCompiler
  [Garbage Collector] as GC
  [Snapshot Mechanism] as Snapshot
  [libuv Event Loop] as Libuv
  [Event Loop] as EventLoop
  [Thread Pool] as ThreadPool
  [Asynchronous I/O] as AsyncIO
  [N-API Binding Layer] as NAPI
  [C++ Bindings] as CppBindings
  [Native Interface] as NativeInterface
}

package "System Technology Layer" {
  [Operating System Interface] as OSInterface
  [Linux Interface] as LinuxAPI
  [Windows Interface] as WindowsAPI
  [macOS Interface] as MacOSAPI
  [Network Protocol Stack] as NetworkStack
  [TCP/UDP] as TCPUDP
  [HTTP/HTTPS] as HTTPStack
  [TLS/SSL] as TLSStack
  [File System Interface] as FSInterface
  [File Operations] as FileOps
  [Directory Operations] as DirOps
  [File Watching] as FileWatch
}

package "Infrastructure Layer" {
  [Build System] as BuildSystem
  [GYP Build] as GYP
  [GN Build] as GN
  [CMake] as CMake
  [Test Framework] as TestFramework
  [Unit Testing] as UnitTest
  [Integration Testing] as IntegrationTest
  [Benchmark] as Benchmark
  [CI/CD System] as CICD
  [Continuous Integration] as CI
  [Continuous Deployment] as CD
  [Automated Testing] as AutoTest
}

package "Technology Standard Layer" {
  [ECMAScript Standard] as ECMAScript
  [HTTP Standard] as HTTPStandard
  [TLS Standard] as TLSStandard
  [Web Standard] as WebStandard
}

' Application Technology Layer Dependencies
NodeCore --> JSAPI
JSAPI --> BuiltinModules
BuiltinModules --> V8Engine
BuiltinModules --> Libuv

' Runtime Technology Layer Dependencies
V8Engine --> JITCompiler
V8Engine --> GC
V8Engine --> Snapshot
Libuv --> EventLoop
Libuv --> ThreadPool
Libuv --> AsyncIO
NAPI --> CppBindings
NAPI --> NativeInterface
CppBindings --> V8Engine
NativeInterface --> Libuv

' System Technology Layer Dependencies
OSInterface --> LinuxAPI
OSInterface --> WindowsAPI
OSInterface --> MacOSAPI
NetworkStack --> TCPUDP
NetworkStack --> HTTPStack
NetworkStack --> TLSStack
FSInterface --> FileOps
FSInterface --> DirOps
FSInterface --> FileWatch

Libuv --> OSInterface
Libuv --> NetworkStack
Libuv --> FSInterface
NodeCore --> OSInterface

' Infrastructure Layer Dependencies
BuildSystem --> GYP
BuildSystem --> GN
BuildSystem --> CMake
TestFramework --> UnitTest
TestFramework --> IntegrationTest
TestFramework --> Benchmark
CICD --> CI
CICD --> CD
CICD --> AutoTest
BuildSystem --> NodeCore
TestFramework --> NodeCore
CICD --> TestFramework

' Technology Standard Layer Relationships
ECMAScript --> V8Engine
HTTPStandard --> HTTPStack
TLSStandard --> TLSStack
WebStandard --> JSAPI

note right of V8Engine
  **V8 Engine Features**
  - Just-In-Time compilation (JIT)
  - Optimized garbage collection
  - Snapshot startup optimization
  - Multi-generational GC strategy
end note

note right of Libuv
  **libuv Event Loop**
  - Cross-platform asynchronous I/O
  - Thread pool management
  - File system operations
  - Network I/O abstraction
end note

note right of BuildSystem
  **Build System**
  - GYP: Traditional build system
  - GN: Modern build system
  - Multi-platform support
  - Incremental builds
end note

note right of OSInterface
  **Cross-Platform Support**
  - Linux: epoll
  - Windows: IOCP
  - macOS: kqueue
  - Unified abstraction interface
end note

@enduml

